validation.validation: There is already a Change Published Admissions Decision Details Event in progress.
You can’t create applications for this academic unit, level, and start date, unless a matching application grouping exists.
The Program of Study must be valid for the Academic Period or Anticipated Start Date.
All Programs of Study must have an Academic Unit that uses the Academic Period Type given.
There must be a valid combination of Program of Study, campus, and anticipated start.
Applicant must have an Admission Decision of Admit with a Decision Published Status of Publicly Available.
You must change either the program of study, start date, location, or gpa in order to proceed.
The Application must be Active and not Matriculated.
You can’t change the admitted program of study to a joint program of study.
You must enter a Program Focus for this Program of Study.
Enter a new Program of Study with the same superior admitting academic unit as the Applied To Program of Study.
